	</image></paragraph>
</tablecell>
<tablecell colspan="" rowspan="">
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3152909" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="6">Double-click a document icon to display the corresponding Help page.</paragraph>
</tablecell>
</tablerow>
</table>

<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3158432" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="7">Use the arrow keys in combination with the Return key to drop down and roll up entries and to open documents.</paragraph>
